  <h1>FakeStack Privacy Policy</h1>
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 0;">High-Performance Database Generator</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    FakeStack is a high-performance database generator library that creates realistic fake data. 
    Available as Python, Node.js, Go packages, and Homebrew formula.
  </p>

  <h2>Information Collected</h2>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>FakeStack collects NO user data.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    FakeStack is a library/CLI tool that runs entirely on your machine. It does not transmit any information 
    to external servers.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Handling</h2>
  <p>All data generated by FakeStack:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Is created locally on your machine</li>
    <li>Stays under your control</li>
    <li>Is never transmitted to our servers</li>
    <li>Can be used however you choose</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>No Telemetry</h2>
  <p>
    FakeStack does not collect:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Usage statistics</li>
    <li>Generated data samples</li>
    <li>Error reports (unless manually submitted)</li>
    <li>Version information</li>
    <li>Any personal information</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Package Distribution</h2>
  <p>
    FakeStack is distributed through standard package managers:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>PyPI (Python Package Index)</li>
    <li>npm (Node Package Manager)</li>
    <li>Homebrew (macOS/Linux)</li>
    <li>GitHub Releases</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    These platforms may collect download statistics. Refer to their privacy policies for details.
  </p>

  <h2>Open Source</h2>
  <p>
    FakeStack is open source. You can verify our privacy claims by inspecting the source code:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>No tracking code</li>
    <li>No network calls</li>
    <li>No data collection</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>None.</strong> FakeStack does not integrate with any third-party services or make any network requests.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy inquiries, contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dps.manit@gmail.com">dps.manit@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p><a href="/privacy">‚Üê Back to Master Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
